import { Box, Flex, FormControl } from "@chakra-ui/react"
import Cour from "../atoms/form/Cour"
import YearInput from "../atoms/form/YearInput"

const Search = () => {
    return (
        <Box>
            <FormControl maxW='150px'>
                <Flex justify='center' align='center'>
                    <YearInput />
                    <Cour />
                </Flex>
            </FormControl>

        </Box>
    )
}

export default Search
